Build the Docker image: 
  docker-cli build|create

Start the development container: 
  docker-cli up|bind

Build and Start the development container: 
  docker-cli start

Conect to the development container: 
  docker-cli exec

Get the Info of the development container: 
  docker-cli info

  Stop the development container: 
  docker-cli stop

Shutdown and remove the development container: 
  docker-cli down|delete

